matlab - notes:
=================================
 mandelbrot set:
	 z, c = matrix with complex coordinates
 	set maximum depth
 	depth times do:
 		compute recursively z
 		if abs(z) < 2, set c to depth-value
 	
 	map values of c to colors and display the
 	image
 	
 image-plot:
 	set(gca, 'YDir', 'normal') flippt die y-Achsen

axis 'normal|square|equal|equal tight' setzt die Achsenproportionen
